data.name: VOP Survey - {{mcpm:ProductName | label:Product Name | description:The Product name that the survey is for}} {{mcpm:SurveyName | label:Survey Name | description:The type of survey that is being sent out. For example, Buy, Leave, or Play }}
{{mcpm:Year|label:Year|description:Year of the survey. Used to organize the DE folders}}
{{mcpm:CampaignType | label:Campaign Type | description: The Campaign Type value used for targeting}}_VOP_GB
{{mcpm:ProductName}} {{mcpm:SurveyName}} VOP GB Audience
data.queryText:
SELECT TOP {{mcpm:GBAudienceSize | label:GB Audience Size | defaultValue:2500}} elig.* FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT
        surv.[hash_acct_id],
		surv.[language_code],
		surv.[country_code],
		surv.[run_date],
		surv.[account_id],
		surv.[sce_region_id],
		surv.[email_address],
		surv.[campaign_type]
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/6818b471-a790-ef11-a5f1-5cba2c7b4968/data/namePrefix}}[VOP Survey Base Audience] AS surv WITH (nolock)
JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/a918b471-a790-ef11-a5f1-5cba2c7b4968/data/namePrefix}}[EMEA_SIEE_ATTRIBUTE_STORE_MASTER] AS atas WITH (nolock)
on surv.email_address = atas.email_address
LEFT JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/b518b471-a790-ef11-a5f1-5cba2c7b4968/data/namePrefix}}[VOP Survey 6 Month Suppression] AS hist WITH (nolock)
on surv.account_id = hist.account_id
WHERE 

atas.optin_1st_party = 'Y'
and (atas.emailable = 1 or atas.emailable is null)
and datediff(year,atas.acct_dob,getdate()) >= 18
and (atas.ban_ind = 0 or atas.ban_ind is null)

AND surv.campaign_type = '{{mcpm:CampaignType}}'
AND surv.country_code = 'GB'
AND surv.language_code is NOT NULL
AND hist.[date_added] IS NULL) AS elig
